android-ndk required (install, add to the system PATH)

-----------------------------------
for android V < lollipop
-----------------------------------
1. cd native

2. nkd-build

-----------------------------------
For android V > lollipop
-----------------------------------

1. uncomment lines in Android.mk:

# LOCAL_CFLAGS += -fPIE
# LOCAL_LDFLAGS += -fPIE -pie


2. cd native

3. nkd-build
